- For January 2023, average temperatures range from 5 to 16°C (41 to 89°F). 
- On May 2023, a high of 17°C (63°F) is forecasted.
- In July, the temperature can reach up to 25°C (77°F), with temperatures ranging from 22°C to 31°C (-4 to -9°F).
- October has a mild temperature range of around 18 to 20°C (68 to 66°F). On the other hand, November and December can have high temperatures in the range of 25 to 27°C (60 to 68°F), but with a low chance of rainfall.
- January and February are known for sunny days that combine with cold winds bringing cool temperatures. There is also a high chance of rain on these two months.

It's important to check the latest weather updates from your location or any relevant weather forecasting apps or websites to get the most accurate information about Yokohama, Japan's climate conditions at any time.
